                <p>
                    <list>
                        <item>“International Commodity Committees scheduled” (<ref target="#pg_6">p.
                                6</ref>)</item>
                        <item>“Efforts to Solve Shipping Shortage” (p. 11)</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">March 5, 1951 (No. 295):</p>
                <p>
                    <list>
